column5: Well, the wife has been all over me to start purging in preparation for the Rec Room/Fishing Lodge. With the Grandkids growing up we don't have a use for these any more.  Free to a good home! Anybody need them??   PM me if interested. Would be great to bring them down to the Swill tomorrow night.
I'll take the church pew Roger ! LOL
LOL Wayne. Just to clarify, the high chair and the stroller!
What is the fine for stealing a church pew?
I think that ya get demoted to Walmatr greeter
Ouch!!  That was a low blow Eh
I got a little one on the way soon so I'll show the wife and see if we can use those and if so, i'll gladly take'em off your hands Roger
